      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I have babied this car since day one, and it is honestly in flawless shape\u2014it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. I'm looking for a new home for my pride and joy, and I promise you won't find one cleaner than this. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
