    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, chips, or swirls, while the interior remains pristine, retaining that distinctive new-car scent. Every surface, from the supple, hand-stitched leather upholstery to the crisp tactile response of the dashboard controls, feels factory-fresh. Mechanically, the car has been maintained with obsessive care, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014smooth, powerful, and silent. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawlessly preserved example that looks and feels untouched by time.",
      "price": 46500.0,
